The result of toString method for each MongoDB java driver method (find, insert, remove etc ..) is collected.

This toString result is a string of json type and length can be very long.

By default only limited length string is allowed, that default length is 50. This option can be used to adjust this value.

If this option's value is set to 0, then the original string will be collected without limit

---

* Default : 50
* Type : Number (Length)
* Restart : Required
* Related Options
    * [enable_mongodb_trace](./agentHelp?key=enable_mongodb_trace&type=1)
    * [enable_mongodb_connection_trace](./agentHelp?key=enable_mongodb_connection_trace&type=1)
    * [mongodb_collect_object_base_elpased_time](./agentHelp?key=mongodb_collect_object_base_elpased_time&type=1)
* Supported Version : 5.0.12